Player Controller Firewall
Player scripts may only own:

Movement, look, interact raycast, PlayerContext, basic physical state

Player scripts must not own:

Puzzle rules, Shadow logic, Pressure calculations, Lore state, Hearth state, Room completion, etc.

Create scene-local controllers under Assets/_Project/Code/Rooms when needed.
